鷹手營子礦區.pinyin: yīng shǒu yíng zi kuàng qū
鷹手營子礦區.definition: Yingshouyingzikuang district of Chengde city 承德市[Cheng2 de2 shi4], Hebei

鷹擊長空.definition: the eagle soars in the sky (citation from Mao Zedong)

鷹星雲.definition: Eagle or Star Queen Nebula M16

鷹派.definition: hawk faction (opposite: 鴿派|鸽派[ge1 pai4], doves); fierce and combative party; war party; warmongers

鷹潭.definition: see 鷹潭市|鹰潭市[Ying1tan2 Shi4]

鷹潭市.definition: Yingtan, prefecture-level city in Jiangxi Province 江西省[Jiang1xi1 Sheng3]

鷹爪翻子拳.definition: Ying Zhua Fan Zi Quan - "Eagle Claw" - Martial Art

鷹犬.definition: hawks and hounds; (fig.) running dogs; hired thugs

鷹狀星雲.definition: Eagle or Star Queen Nebula M16

鷹雕.definition: variant of 鷹鵰|鹰雕[ying1 diao1]

鷹鴞.definition: (bird species of China) brown boobook; brown hawk-owl (Ninox scutulata)

鷹鵑.definition: (bird species of China) large hawk-cuckoo (Hierococcyx sparverioides)

鷹鵰.definition: (bird species of China) mountain hawk-eagle; Hodgson's hawk-eagle (Nisaetus nipalensis)
